### Install
> pip install ez-otlp

### Usage Instructions
##### In your project
```python
# env
# EZ_ENDPOINT = http://host.docker.internal:4317/v1/traces
# EZ_RESOURCE_SERVICE_NAME = ez-otlp

from ez_otlp import EZ_OTLP

otlp = EZ_OTLP(log=["logging", "structlog"])
```
##### Run template.py
```bash
docker-compose up
```

#### locally hosted SigNoz
> http://localhost:3301/
```bash
cd signoz
docker-compose up -d
```

